        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) Die sabati que est de mense octubris, in <rs key="#Cities"
                            >civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Domus #Bishops" ref="#places/9">Brixia</placeName>
                        in <rs key="#Domus">domo</rs>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>, presencia <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum hominum</rs> quorum nomina subter
                        leguntur, concessit domnus <persName
                            key="#Cardinals #Bishops #Churches #Witness" ref="#people/2180"
                            >Armannus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Cardinals">cardinalis</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Cardinals" ref="#juridical_persons/1100">Romane
                            Ecclesie</orgName> et episcopus suprascripte <orgName
                            key="#Bishops #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1425">Sancte Brixiensis eccesie</orgName>,
                        consenciente <persName
                            key="#siblingOf #milesOf #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            >Adegerio</persName> et <persName
                            key="#siblingOf #milesOf #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            >Ardiciono</persName> seu <persName
                            key="#siblingOf #milesOf #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            >Magifredo</persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">germani</rs>
                        <rs key="#milesOf">milites</rs> domnus predicti Armani episcopi <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Abbots #Monks #Churches #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti inter Padum et
                            Ilarionem</orgName> et suis <rs key="#Monks">monahis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2066">Sancti
                            Viti</orgName> que est posita in loco <placeName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#places/2475">Medule</placeName> ubi habitare et <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs> facere et Deo servire et vivere ibi
                        secundum regulam Sancti Benedicti et <rs key="#Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            >duas pecias de terra aratorias</rs> iuris suprascripti episcopii
                        positas prope ipsam ecclesiam faciendo cambium cum suprascriptis militibus,
                        silicet Adegerio et Magifredo seu Ardeciono per parabolam et voluntatem
                        ipsorum; et faciant iam dictus abbas et monahi de hanc ecclesia et de hanc
                        terra quicquid voluerint sicut supra legitur salvo onore Sancte predicte
                        Brixiensis ecclesie sine contradicione quin suprascripti Adegerio et
                        Magifredi seu Ardecioni suorumque heredum. Factum est hoc anno ab
                        incarnacione domini nostri Iesu Christi millesimo octuagesimo septimo,
                        suprascripto die et mense, indicione undecima. Ego Herimannus Sancte Romane
                        Ecclesie cardinalis confirmo. Et ego <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Witness #Priests">sacerdos</rs> laudo et confirmo. + Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Advocatus"><name ref="Oddo">Oddo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus">avocatus</rs> interfui. (S.) Ego <persName
                            key="#Notary #Judge #Writer"><name ref="Otto">Otto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> rogatus <rs
                            key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et interfui. </ab>
